ch.iserver.ace.algorithm
Interface Algorithm

All Known Subinterfaces:
AlgorithmWrapper
All Known Implementing Classes:
AlgorithmWrapperImpl, Jupiter
public interface Algorithm

This interface is the basic interface every OT algorithm implementation must implement. It contains methods for generating requests for an operation, receiving requests and for site management.
